Deploy generated CRD files to the Kubernetes cluster.
When platform API credentials are configured (mcp-runtime auth login), manifests
are applied through POST /api/runtime/servers without kubectl. Otherwise kubectl
apply is used and requires a working kubeconfig.

Usage:
  mcp-runtime pipeline deploy [flags]

Flags:
      --dir string         Directory containing CRD files (default "manifests")
  -h, --help               help for deploy
      --namespace string   Namespace to deploy to (overrides metadata)

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging
